    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use especially with reference to sculpture or architectural and infrastructural elements, such as columns, walls, or signs, that stand alone. To refer to buildings standing alone, prefer "detached."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese sobre todo con referencia a escultura o elementos arquitectónicos e infraestructurales, como columnas, paredes, o señales, que se auto soportan. Para referirse a edificios que se levantan separadamente, prefiera "separado."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vooral te gebruiken met betrekking tot beeldhouwwerken of architectonische en infrastructurele elementen zoals zuilen, muren of borden, die alleen staan. Gebruik bij voorkeur 'vrijstaand (positioneel kenmerk gebouw)' voor gebouwen die alleen staan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>特別用於指稱雕塑或建築物及基礎設施，例如獨立的柱子、牆壁或招牌。指稱獨立的建築物，偏好使用「分離的」一詞。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
